        <title>
            What Smacky's Guides try to be
        </title>
        <section id="entertaining">
            <title>
                Smacky's Guides try to be... entertaining
            </title>
            <p>
                You'll laugh! You'll cry!
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="informative">
            <title>
                Smacky's Guides try to be... informative
            </title>
            <p>
                You'll learn!
            </p>
        </section>
